    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特点：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多样的互动物体和障碍</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时尚、极简的艺术风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >难度逐渐增加，挑战多样化</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>旋转镜子以放大光束：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244460/extras/4ccb6eac0840a085c43f8abeb6d768ef.poster.avif?t=1727785351\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244460/extras/4ccb6eac0840a085c43f8abeb6d768ef.webm?t=1727785351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244460/extras/4ccb6eac0840a085c43f8abeb6d768ef.mp4?t=1727785351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>避免受到光影响的障碍：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244460/extras/bb2f0edb762d18cd3b08a13f8ae775da.poster.avif?t=1727785351\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244460/extras/bb2f0edb762d18cd3b08a13f8ae775da.webm?t=1727785351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244460/extras/bb2f0edb762d18cd3b08a13f8ae775da.mp4?t=1727785351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有不同类型的烟。好的。坏的：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244460/extras/d809867fee47610c69710659f11a0355.poster.avif?t=1727785351\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244460/extras/d809867fee47610c69710659f11a0355.webm?t=1727785351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244460/extras/d809867fee47610c69710659f11a0355.mp4?t=1727785351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>按下开关。旋转双墙：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244460/extras/538a78dc65a0170ba4e03c8c31fce06e.poster.avif?t=1727785351\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244460/extras/538a78dc65a0170ba4e03c8c31fce06e.webm?t=1727785351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244460/extras/538a78dc65a0170ba4e03c8c31fce06e.mp4?t=1727785351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
